OL,6,FA corrupt border officer, arrested for
OL,7,Fhelping a London-based organised crime
OL,8,Fgang smuggle drugs through Portsmouth,
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for two years.
OL,11,FKevin Smith, 38, was detained by
OL,12,Fofficers from the NCA's Anti-
OL,13,FCorruption Unit at work in the port as
OL,14,Fpart of a joint operation with the
OL,15,FMetropolitan Police Service and Border
OL,16,FForce.
