OL,3,CCorrupt border officer jailed for
OL,4,Chelping crime gang smuggle drugs
OL,6,FEarlier that day Smith had allowed
OL,7,Fdrug smuggler Caprice Thompson, 46,
OL,8,Ffrom Brixton, to pass through his
OL,9,FBorder Force booth, having arrived on
OL,10,Fa ferry from France. Her car contained
OL,11,F15 kilos of MDMA worth around #400,000.
OL,13,FAs she drove back towards London she
OL,14,Fwas stopped by Met officers who
OL,15,Farrested her and found the drugs in
OL,16,Fthe boot.
