OL,6,FTwo other members of the crime group
OL,7,Fwere also arrested ` ringleader David
OL,8,FJohnson, 51, and Sinan Baki, 49, both
OL,9,Ffrom Clapham. Further drugs were
OL,10,Frecovered from their properties.
OL,12,FThe joint operation followed an
OL,13,Finvestigation into the crime group by
OL,14,Fthe Met, who brought in the NCA once
OL,15,Fit became clear a corrupt insider was
OL,16,Fin contact with Johnson.
