OL,6,FThe NCA put Smith under surveillance,
OL,7,Fand obtained CCTV evidence that the
OL,8,Fformer prison officer engaged in a
OL,9,Fnumber of face to face meetings in
OL,10,FPortsmouth with Johnson in the run-up
OL,11,Fto the smuggling attempt.
OL,13,FSmith and Johnson's relationship had
OL,14,Fstarted whilst Smith was working as a
OL,15,Fprison officer in the prison where
OL,16,FJohnson was serving a sentence for
OL,17,Fdrugs importation.
