OL,3,CCorrupt border officer jailed for
OL,4,Chelping crime gang smuggle drugs
OL,6,FFollowing Smith's arrest NCA officers
OL,7,Falso recovered a mobile phone which he
OL,8,Fhad used to exchange encrypted
OL,9,Fmessages with Johnson.
OL,11,FJohnson pleaded guilty to importing
OL,12,Fclass A drugs, and Baki admitted
OL,13,Fpossessing class A drugs with intent
OL,14,Fto supply.
OL,16,FSmith admitted a charge of misconduct
OL,17,Fin a public office. He was cleared of
OL,18,Fdrug smuggling charges during a trial
OL,19,Fat Kingston Crown Court that also saw
OL,20,FThompson convicted of the same offence
OL,21,Fon 4 April 2024.
