OL,6,FOn Friday (7 June) a judge at the same
OL,7,Fcourt sentenced Smith to two years in
OL,8,Fprison. Ringleader Johnson was given a
OL,9,F12-year jail term, Baki got eight
OL,10,Fyears, and smuggler Thompson was
OL,11,Fhanded a seven year sentence.
OL,13,FDave Rock from the NCA's Anti-
OL,14,FCorruption Unit said: "Fortunately
OL,15,Fthis type of corruption is relatively
OL,16,Frare but it does present a real threat
OL,17,Fto the security of the public, which
OL,18,Fis why we treat it as a priority.
