OL,6,F"People like Kevin Smith are
OL,7,Finvaluable to organised crime groups,
OL,8,Fas they can use their access and
OL,9,Fknowledge to aid their criminal
OL,10,Fendeavors.
OL,12,F"This operation demonstrated the
OL,13,Fexcellent co-operation between the
OL,14,FNCA, Met Police and Border Force who
OL,15,Fworked together to stop this gang in
OL,16,Ftheir tracks and prevent class A drugs
OL,17,Freaching the streets."
